le compatible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/250e3f183f68058f422c0ed5fc42a6bd.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span><br><br>You control your lights with drumsticks!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/697498afab6066c53450717ac9c4758e.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span><br><br>9 musicians with these instruments: electric guitar, drums, bass guitar, music keyboard, piano, violin, bongo drum, trumpet and saxophone.<br><br>18 singers of different styles in two genres, female and male.<br>K-pop, pop, classic pop, rap, reggae, ballad, rock, guitarist and pianist.<br><br>9 fun dancers and chorus girls to set the stage:<br>Dancing girl, dancing boy, bear, happy face, led costume, female choir, male choir, mysterious choristers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897400/extras/76a48824671896232f486b7c5fd5c601.avif?t=1671546015\" width=600 height=204 /></span>",
